These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Flower: azalea, zinnia, dahlia, poppy
1. Flower:zinnia is in an odd position##4
2. Flower:poppy is between Flower:azalea and Flower:zinnia##2
3. Flower:poppy is on the right of Flower:azalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Flower   | azalea | poppy | zinnia | dahlia |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Transport: boat, subway, motorbike, roller
1. Transport:boat is on the left of Transport:roller##1
2. Transport:subway is in an odd position##4
3. Transport:subway is on the left or right of Transport:boat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Transport   | subway | boat | roller | motorbike |

 #################################
 
