.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Transport: helicopter, quad-bike, tram, roller
1. Transport:quad-bike == Transport:quad-bike##1
2. Transport:roller is on the left or right of Transport:tram##3
3. Transport:tram is on the far left or far right##3
4. Transport:helicopter is in an even position##4
5. Transport:roller is on the left of Transport:quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | tram | roller | quad-bike | helicopter |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
Color: grey, yellow, orange, white
1. Color:orange is in an odd position##4
2. Color:white is on the left of Color:orange##1
3. Color:orange is on the left or right of Color:yellow##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Color   | grey | white | orange | yellow |

 